{"tid":1110660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地班撚樣仆街啦, 留意埋偽人無聊野, 都唔理梁天琦","createTime":"2019-04-16T15:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T01:48:41.000Z","uid":76310,"like":29,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d28b496c28cf5357860f206577187dfa9c99539c","tid":1110660,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T15:34:48.000Z","msg":"你地班撚樣仆街啦, 留意埋偽人無聊野, 都唔理梁天琦<br />\n偽人邊個同邊個攪野關你撚事, 無聊野<br />\n但梁天琦為香港人出聲, 無人理, 無人關心<br />\n將來香港強国化, 有黑心食物, 又整單邊個偽人偷食邊個偽人, 或者強拆, 又整單邊個偽人搭上邊個偽人, 呢D無聊野. 到時希望你地食到食物中毒, 然後無人理<br />\n<br />\n邊個幫香港人出頭, 香港人吊佢攪事, 攪攪震<br />\n留意埋D無聊野, 都唔關心自己切身利益<br />\n將來香港快些強国化, 到時快些一齊仆街"},{"pid":"2bca0e5762e21eb6ec191a043974fb0bdd2b324c","tid":1110660,"uid":7529,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T15:43:01.000Z","msg":"今屆英超亞軍係唔係有史以來積分最高？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1107802\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1107802</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9bf8a4a10b809b677d0b284f11e9a0bcbda2cb84","tid":1110660,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T15:47:07.000Z","msg":"逃犯條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35337a160f8cda77c45f22493ff8240c26df54f8","tid":1110660,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T15:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ca4ee8154edc2d5fee6565ab4abdd898687e03","tid":1110660,"uid":7678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T15:50:27.000Z","msg":"事實上，而家係d 香港人會主動送自己上深圳食元素表。就算抗爭到、爭取到、主流香港人係唔會領情。"},{"pid":"c32776bf0ea7e7d9167f64d66b060cfee2de11d2","tid":1110660,"uid":247924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T15:50:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"